OL,3,CFree prom shop opens for young school
OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Ann
OL,7,FO'Connor has been to a project making
OL,8,FProm more manageable for parents
OL,10,FA free prom shop has opened in
OL,11,FSalford, acting like a fairy godmother
OL,12,Fand make sure everyone has the chance
OL,13,Fto dress to impress on prom night.
OL,15,FThe shop in Walkden is designed to
OL,16,Fmake prom shopping more affordable,
OL,17,Fpassing on free dresses that have been
OL,18,Fdonated and would have cost hundreds
OL,19,Fof pounds.
