OL,3,CFree prom shop opens for young school
OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FBecky Marshall set up the service in
OL,7,Fher living room last year and has now
OL,8,Fjoined forces with community charity
OL,9,FSalford Step into Action.
OL,11,FShe said: "There's no criteria, we
OL,12,Fdon't require parents to be on
OL,13,Fbenefits. We believe that every young
OL,14,Fperson should go to prom."
OL,16,FStudent Leona Retford used the service
OL,17,Flast year, and came back to encourage
OL,18,Fothers to come and get their dream
OL,19,Fdress for the big night.
