OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FShe said: "It's really heartwarming
OL,7,Fbecause when it gets close to prom
OL,8,Fthere is a pressure to find a dress
OL,9,Ffor hundreds of pounds.
OL,11,F"When I found out about this place I
OL,12,Fwas dead happy and it relieved the
OL,13,Fpressure.
OL,15,FShe said the feeling of not going
OL,16,Fwould have been "gutting".
OL,18,FProm dresses are often worn for one
OL,19,Fnight, so Becky wants them to be put
OL,20,Fto use for other people, rather than
OL,21,Fbeing left in wardrobes.
